Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.80,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the staff around \NYunosagi are very capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.23,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't expected you to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring such large-scale equipment with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:47.18,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,The cameraman works in \Nthe special effects department,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.03,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,so he's actually better at filming stunts like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.20,Default,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's film the next scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.20,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment, Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.31,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.59,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.02,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:18.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.51,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.77,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Mom? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.94,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling homesick,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after your recent visit home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.86,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me get straight to the point. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.14,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You received an offer for a movie to be shot at the inn, didn't you? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.16,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.41,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't accept that offer, did you? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.25,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you haven't accepted it yet, that's good.  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.06,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I've left Enishi in charge of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.47,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.39,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm telling you, \Nsomething is fishy about the whole thing! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.92,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can call it off right now \Nby just opening your mouth! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:04:00.22,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,This time I don't plan \Non interfering at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.57,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, Mom! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.60,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about \Ninheriting this inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.92,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, no, \NEnishi will be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.34,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.18,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enishi will be the one \Nwho inherits Kissuiso, Mom. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.98,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I've just said something \Npretty foolish, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.99,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't foolish. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.86,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it is all in the past now.  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:28.45,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bye. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.48,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.68,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.43,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.26,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,We were watching you from up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.39,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that they're shooting a film here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.14,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What you were doing \Nwas very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:12.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, \Nwe'll still be at your service as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.06,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how well \Nyou've been taking care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.38,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who jumped \Nfrom the building just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.14,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,My heart nearly stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might want to refrain from \Nwatching what's coming next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's a wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.90,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.15,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.29,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What's this movie supposed to be about, precisely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.76,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The proposal said, \N"waitresses in their youth."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yuina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.51,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:49.98,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That all the madam managers in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the union don't like \Nthis upcoming movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:57.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think everyone gets a little
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uneasy when trying out something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.13,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're \Nnot the ones staging it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:02.99,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you be jealous if someone became
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,successful at doing something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.00,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, people say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there aren't exactly many \Nscenes in this film where lots
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of madam managers appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All the madam managers can go to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hot spring for a work trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.98,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,And then they all become zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.07,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.61,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,A meal for two in the Paulownia Room, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.80,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this to the Wisteria Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.64,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The meal with the red tag
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has no green onions in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:42.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.38,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:44.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.89,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Explains what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A customer in the Wisteria Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kept staring at my face earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.22,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.73,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we're here, we'll be shooting for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.69,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.62,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Mr. Isami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.90,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.49,Default,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Expect great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:19.00,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning this on, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.85,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.21,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it is a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.38,Default,Madam2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.16,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,I had my suspicions from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.01,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,A scam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This has got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.36,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,The folks at Kissuiso have \Nreally done it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.61,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako! Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.57,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't managed \Nto contact Mr. Isami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.46,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I only received an \Ne-mail from him saying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the project had been called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.12,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try calling him again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.45,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I had my suspicions \Nabout this from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.58,Default,Enisih,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.31,Default,Enisih,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me this {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.71,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't rush the payment and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only pay them once you've \Nconfirmed that it's safe."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.08,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the contract is under your name, Enishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.64,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who told me \Nabout this in the first place, Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.44,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.93,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.32,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen \Nto the young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.89,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.26,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I did hear he paid them a lot of money, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.03,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for \Nlistening to that dumb woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.53,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.29,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,"Isami Tetsuo."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.39,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,The characters in his \Nname must stand for,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stepping out of the ring and \Nfollowing someone's mistake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.09,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll peel the white radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that Tohru was tactless,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still think that a good \Nchef can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.90,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.13,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you hear? \NThe movie's been called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad we didn't get to act in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.16,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.84,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.20,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that this would \Nbe the summer break to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi was also really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.78,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I rushed here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I thought \NKissuiso would be in a mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.41,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.66,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you only just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.91,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.96,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't know much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:06.99,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.03,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is just me talking to myself. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.94,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isami Tetsuo. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.62,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's run from debt twice \Nin his life before, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.94,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he was laid off by \Nthe people in his industry.  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:20.48,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure he's used \Nthe money to pay off his debts,  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.47,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so it'll be too difficult \Nto get it back. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.72,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The actors and the staff who \Nmistakenly got involved with him {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.58,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are probably going to be \Nin trouble for a while. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.16,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry for the sudden call. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.25,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sis-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:42.85,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.83,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't plan on crying over spilled milk, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I still don't believe \Nthat what I was trying{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to do was wrong. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.77,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.25,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,But just remember that the \Ninvestors are responsible for the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.36,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.03,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.02,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,But you're also responsible for \Nthe staff and the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.10,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're strict as usual. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:09.45,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, \Neveryone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:13.13,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks for the info, Sis. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.65,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.83,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry flavor is the best after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.41,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd clean the \Narea surrounding the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.13,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But the movie's been called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've been cleaning the pool every day recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's sort of become one of my tasks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand not cleaning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.24,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:57.21,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you two are going as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:58.25,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.19,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Minko's already gone ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.47,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,For the same reason as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.97,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,That pool isn't only for the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.98,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.39,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:20.13,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.46,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.61,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot of things \Nwhich I need to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.98,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know. I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.00,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to \Nbabysit you any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.58,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"Babysit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were partners...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.99,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:41.16,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's \Nresponsible for this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.02,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.84,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,An adviser. Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:49.35,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But, Takako, we handed him \Nthe contract together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.61,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We discussed it and decided together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.03,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. That-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.14,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.14,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:04.61,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go and ask \Nyour beloved sister for help then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.86,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare say bad \Nthings about my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.64,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly like Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.12,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.88,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it was a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.58,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.71,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.41,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.31,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a woman \Nwho's able to strike back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.30,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about who's responsible \Nhere won't help us at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.84,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to show \Nme how cool you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.10,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The Takako I always see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.73,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"We strike back."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"I shall"{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.35,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:41.36,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"We shall return!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.27,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you spouting now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.49,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it's English doesn't mean\Nyou can just say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.40,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,She's right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.81,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I said, don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.35,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.47,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.85,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, just one more time-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:17.92,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Takako-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:18.72,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.00,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.67,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.78,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to \Nhold on or let go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.67,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.50,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.05,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.33,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.31,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Max limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:59.77,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.94,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, young master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.29,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.52,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.27,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let this be over yet, do you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.43,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.15,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,For God's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.29,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.61,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What is your {\i1}problem{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.63,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my battle gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.19,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Battle gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:35.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! And you're paying for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,They were expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:41.02,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,So you were wearing your battle gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:41.70,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.37,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, they were expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.66,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were serious, Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:47.99,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:49.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.27,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Takako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:54.44,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not at fault. \NYou tried your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.24,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.53,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I've always said that your independent and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,peculiar way of thinking is \None of your major flaws-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.87,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.52,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, and don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.30,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start again together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.56,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.38,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.84,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Only thinking about themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.40,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't watch any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.02,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:49.00,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.58,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.04,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:57.87,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd act like \Na mother for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.31,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso's got a lot to take care of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they brought this upon themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.58,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,They were walking on air, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.65,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:20.16,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I did walk on air when \NI leaped from the second story window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.53,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Bang! Bang! Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.85,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,There was also a scene like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.20,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to hear the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.90,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be best
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I let you, the representatives of Yunosagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:45.80,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,know of our current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.12,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The meal for the Wave Room is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.02,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is the sashimi for the \NCrane Room still not ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.19,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.42,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.95,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.36,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.21,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.65,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,How's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.21,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,They're all doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:23.62,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been the one to go and explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.85,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, and I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:30.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But Ms. Kawajiri really had \NKissuiso on her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,and did her best to make things work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.53,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kawajiri will have to take \Nher share of the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.01,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.88,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.53,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me "Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:46.74,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:50.43,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm not defending her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.87,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She really was trying her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.84,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.21,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that you've grown enough to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to defend someone so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.03,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I never understood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether you were simply \Nstubborn or just clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.52,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about the piano lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.30,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,During high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously thought that being
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,able to play an instrument \Nwould get me the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:29.52,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But you kept refusing to take \Nlessons in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:34.07,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,If only you'd put a collar on me \Nand taken me to those lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:37.60,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,my teenage life would have \Nbeen a lot different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.46,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You were a terrible swimmer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.33,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I still am, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.39,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.40,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.78,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.41,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:56.20,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny looking cloud...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 17\NPool on the Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a mermaid princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:46.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't admire a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:49.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,because... land is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 18\NA Mermaid Princess and a Shell Bra
